WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:04.959
Good morning, family. I'm excited to be with you all again today. I have a word.

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:15.962
You know, I usually come on here and have a lot of negative words—what people would call doom and gloom.

00:00:15.963 --> 00:00:31.026
But today, I have the opportunity to give you a positive word, an uplifting word, an encouraging word that people have been believing for decades and decades, maybe thousands of years.

00:00:31.027 --> 00:00:47.206
You know, cancer has been around for a long, long time. The Lord spoke to me whenever I was praying, and He opened my eyes in the realm of the spirit.

00:00:47.207 --> 00:01:02.845
He said, "Brandon, I'm bringing the cure for cancer."I saw a man in a lab coat, and he was pouring some stuff in a jar.

00:01:02.846 --> 00:01:17.913
All of a sudden, Holy Ghost revelation came to his mind, and he saw it—whatever it was, I don't know, I'm not a chemist.

00:01:17.914 --> 00:01:25.438
He put it together, then he looked at it underneath the microscope and found it by the Holy Spirit.

00:01:25.439 --> 00:01:32.178
The Lord spoke to me and said this man is not even a born-again Christian.

00:01:32.179 --> 00:01:43.377
He warned me and said, "Brandon, I'm bringing this to pass because people have cried out to Me for a long time.

00:01:43.378 --> 00:02:40.702
They have been believing for their relatives and people that have gone home too early."This has been a plague on humanity, and the Lord said, "Brandon, I'm bringing a cure for this."He said, "I'm going to put My foot on this, and it will become like plagues of the past that were completely eradicated, things we don't hear about anymore, like leprosy or tuberculosis—things that were very deadly in the early 1800s before they came out with the vaccinations."Some of those viruses back then were very serious, but now, with antibiotics, it's able to be taken care of a lot easier.

00:02:40.703 --> 00:02:49.838
The Lord told me this will be a preventative and a cure at the same time.

00:02:49.839 --> 00:03:03.439
He said people can take this and will never even have it in their body, and the people that have it will automatically be healed; it will just leave them.

00:03:03.440 --> 00:03:12.542
The way He presented it to me was that it didn't matter what kind of cancer it was, it would be gone.

00:03:12.543 --> 00:03:24.150
It wouldn't be a long, drawn-out process; it would just instantaneously start to turn the ship around.

00:03:24.151 --> 00:03:42.393
The Lord said to me it would not be a medication; it would be like a supplement. That's how simple He said it is.

00:03:42.394 --> 00:04:03.279
He said, "Son, it's something so simple coming from the earth."Whenever they put these things together, it will create the combination that it takes for the cure.

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:09.354
It's designed perfectly for it, but it's divine from God. Does that make sense?

00:04:09.355 --> 00:04:26.365
I'm doing the best I can with this, but what I saw in the spirit was the Lord telling me that cancer would become a thing of the past.

00:04:26.366 --> 00:04:53.016
There would be government things that would rise up to try to stop it, but the Lord would put His hand on it to stop them because He said this has been something that has been dealt with for too long.

00:04:53.017 --> 00:04:57.960
I was so filled with the Holy Spirit whenever He gave me this word.

00:04:57.961 --> 00:05:09.659
I couldn't wait to come on here and tell you what the Lord is telling me is coming for the world.

00:05:09.660 --> 00:05:18.909
It's because God so loved the world that He gave His one and only begotten son, that whosoever believes in Him should not perish but have everlasting life.

00:05:18.910 --> 00:05:27.284
He gave salvation to everybody. That's the way God is—He's not just about Christians; He's about loving everybody.

00:05:27.285 --> 00:05:35.375
He wants everybody to come to repentance so they don't have to go to hell.

00:05:35.376 --> 00:06:00.622
Bottom line, folks. He's not up there with a big stick hitting people in the head. He wants to show you His love and His kindness.

00:06:00.623 --> 00:06:09.185
He gave His son, who died for us and rose again on the third day, and He is seated right now at the right hand of the Father.

00:06:09.186 --> 00:06:15.437
I'm telling you, He's coming back again, but He has a present for all of us.

00:06:15.438 --> 00:06:19.631
Jesus took all those things on the cross for us; we don't have to have it now.

00:06:19.632 --> 00:06:27.051
But some people don't have the faith to believe for healing, or the cure for cancer, or diabetes.

00:06:27.052 --> 00:06:27.151
Jesus paid the price for everybody to have health and healing.

00:06:27.152 --> 00:06:51.062
Sometimes He uses medicine to help folks that don't know how to believe by faith, and that's just the mercy of God.

00:06:51.063 --> 00:07:03.033
What I'm trying to tell you is that He told me He is giving a supernatural wisdom to this man that was mixing stuff.

00:07:03.034 --> 00:07:09.393
I saw the company name and where it was located. I'm praying over it still; you can pray with me.

00:07:09.394 --> 00:07:17.154
I'm not going to give that out yet because I don't want any demonic attacks trying to come against this.

00:07:17.154 --> 00:07:34.467
I believe God is going to do what He said He would do. The company does exist.

00:07:34.468 --> 00:07:43.536
They are working with supplements right now, but I don't even know if they know about it yet.

00:07:43.537 --> 00:07:50.779
I see things in part and hear in part, sometimes years in advance.

00:07:50.780 --> 00:08:10.598
There have been times whenever He has told me to pray for companies that didn't even exist yet. He'll give me a name and spell it out in a vision.

00:08:10.599 --> 00:08:27.901
I'll try to Google it, and it doesn't exist yet, but He says, "I want you to intercede for this name."So I pray over the name for months or years.

00:08:27.902 --> 00:08:42.070
All of a sudden, He'll say, "Brandon, that company has been birthed and it is existing now.

00:08:42.071 --> 00:08:57.154
I want you to go Google it,"and it's there. I'll look at their mission, and it's usually for health and wellness.

00:08:57.154 --> 00:09:06.611
Then I see other companies try to attack with lawsuits because the devil doesn't want people to be restored.

00:09:06.612 --> 00:09:30.896
His mission is to kill, steal, and destroy, but the Lord said, "I have come that you might have life and life more abundantly."He wants us to live in the overflow of life with joy unspeakable and full of glory.

00:09:30.897 --> 00:10:03.197
There are dark days and hard times because we're in the last of the last seconds before Jesus Christ comes back, but I'm telling you, folks, there is an anointing on healing, deliverance, growing out limbs, and creative miracles that we have not even yet seen.

00:10:03.198 --> 00:10:27.863
Good days are coming; blessed days are coming. Another thing the Lord showed me: there's going to be Black Swan events coming—distractions from the Deep State—that we'll have to pray against.

00:10:27.864 --> 00:10:34.907
The enemy is trying to distract and cause things not to happen that God wants to happen.

00:10:34.908 --> 00:10:58.195
But we all know the devil's defeated and we have authority over him. I told you all about EVs and the green agenda being pushed.

00:10:58.196 --> 00:11:14.222
I saw an article stating that people were losing interest in EVs because of range anxiety.

00:11:14.223 --> 00:11:28.872
The Holy Ghost warned me that events are going to come to try to discourage people from gasoline and sway them toward EVs because of gas prices going up again.

00:11:28.873 --> 00:11:37.635
I saw gas prices going high and lines for gasoline, like in the 1970s.

00:11:37.636 --> 00:11:55.492
The Lord warned me about lines for gasoline because they couldn't get the gas into the stations.

00:11:55.493 --> 00:12:13.647
These things are trying to manifest again. Just letting you know, this is something to be on alert about.

00:12:13.648 --> 00:12:34.836
These men's agendas are going to fall. They think they're gods, but I'm telling you, Dad is about ready to spank some rears.

00:12:34.837 --> 00:12:43.977
I saw a man that I pray about a lot who is over a lot of dark agenda.

00:12:43.978 --> 00:13:03.697
The Lord warned me, "Brandon, I'm going to deal with that, and it's going to be something that happens overnight."I looked up the man's age; he's in his elderly years.

00:13:03.698 --> 00:13:42.015
He's going to go home soon. Judgment is coming. I saw him being dealt with, and it was very concerning to me because I know this man is not born again.

00:13:42.016 --> 00:13:56.363
There are going to be people in high positions that God is going to start to deal with, and they'll be here one minute and gone the next.

00:13:56.364 --> 00:14:05.165
The Lord warned me that there's an acceleration of seed time and harvest.

00:14:05.166 --> 00:14:14.471
People walking in darkness and evil will reap what they sow.

00:14:14.471 --> 00:14:22.802
There's going to be an acceleration of good and an acceleration of bad.

00:14:22.803 --> 00:14:31.240
When we see these people who have been sowing bad, they're going to sow and reap what they've sown.

00:14:31.241 --> 00:15:07.951
But when you've sown good things—your tithes, your offerings, your time, taking care of the widow and the orphan—you're going to start reaping an amazing harvest.

00:15:07.952 --> 00:15:27.073
Supernatural increase is coming to your house. You're going to start to see the manifestation of what you sowed within a couple of hours because seed time and harvest is accelerating.

00:15:27.074 --> 00:15:44.182
We're also going to see the darkness start to reap what they've sown: perversion, sex trafficking, drugs, and prostitution.

00:15:44.183 --> 00:16:06.796
God said, "I'm bringing judgment on this stuff."You see these people practicing evil and think they're getting away with it?

00:16:06.797 --> 00:16:18.638
They're not. Payday is coming, and it's going to be a bad payday for these people.

00:16:18.639 --> 00:16:34.330
If you're one of them, you better turn before you burn. It's time for you to repent and ask the Lord Jesus Christ to forgive you.

00:16:34.331 --> 00:17:10.864
If you confess your sins, He is faithful and just to forgive you. Your time is running out.

00:17:10.865 --> 00:17:28.654
I had an email from a man in Australia who was raised in an abusive Christian home.

00:17:28.655 --> 00:17:46.519
He died and went to hell, and he saw all the things in hell. He was tormented beyond comprehension.

00:17:46.520 --> 00:18:02.319
Hell is real, and so is heaven. Out of His mercy, the Lord brought this man back, and he is now born-again and spirit-filled.

00:18:02.320 --> 00:18:24.662
But time is running out. As in the days of Noah, so will it be when the Son of Man returns.

00:18:24.663 --> 00:18:43.801
The door of the Ark is getting ready to close. There are people who mock me and call me a false prophet, but I don't care.

00:18:43.802 --> 00:19:05.462
I'm going to keep telling you: Jesus is coming. They mocked Noah until that first drop hit their forehead.

00:19:05.463 --> 00:19:40.735
The time is coming when the Rapture occurs and we're changed in the twinkling of an eye.

00:19:40.736 --> 00:19:56.976
You can turn your life around right now. Run from sin, run from the devil.

00:19:56.977 --> 00:20:05.977
Some people feel like they have a devil and need deliverance. You should know the truth, and the truth will set you free.

00:20:05.978 --> 00:20:20.169
Find scriptures about being free—that "the wicked one touches you not."Feed your spirit.

00:20:20.170 --> 00:20:32.274
The more you get in the Word and renew your mind, the more you will be set free.

00:20:32.275 --> 00:20:46.172
Smith Wigglesworth used to carry a New Testament in his pocket and read it every 15 minutes.

00:20:46.173 --> 00:21:08.036
That's how you do it. You've got to fill yourself up because we leak. This is what's going to set you free from demonic spirits.

00:21:08.037 --> 00:21:31.674
If you don't fill yourself up with the Word, they're going to come back with eight more of their friends.

00:21:31.675 --> 00:22:08.360
Stay free, renew your mind, and take communion daily. Father, I thank You for every person watching.

00:22:08.361 --> 00:22:29.193
I thank You, Lord, that they are healed and whole. They are delivered from cancer, diabetes, and heart disease.

00:22:29.194 --> 00:22:34.894
You put it on my heart this morning to pray for people believing for babies.

00:22:34.895 --> 00:23:01.462
I thank You, Lord, that in 2024, they will have that child. If You did it for Abraham and Sarah, You will do it for them.

00:23:01.463 --> 00:23:16.117
We speak to the seed of the man and call it fertile. I speak to women's ovaries and their Fallopian tubes.

00:23:16.118 --> 00:24:04.927
Their vines will not cast fruit before the time. I see someone about to have a baby boy.

00:24:04.928 --> 00:24:25.398
I thank You, Lord, for new kidneys, new hearts, new discs, and new tendons.

00:24:25.399 --> 00:24:44.350
We curse infection in prostates and command it to go in the name of Jesus.

00:24:44.351 --> 00:25:14.379
We thank You for deliverance from demonic spirits. I take authority over bipolar disorder and PTSD.

00:25:14.380 --> 00:26:14.412
I call healing over their minds. I saw someone being tormented in their sleep with recurring nightmares. You are delivered from that in the name of Jesus.

00:26:14.413 --> 00:26:34.882
I hear the Spirit of the Lord say, "Anoint your bed and your home with oil."This is a demonic spirit sent to torment you.

00:26:34.883 --> 00:26:45.526
Anoint your forehead before you go to bed and put a bloodline over your mind.

00:26:45.527 --> 00:26:53.121
He gives His beloved sweet sleep. This is just a little imp devil; it's not a principality.

00:26:53.122 --> 00:26:56.321
It looks like a little monkey in the spirit realm. Get it out of here.

00:26:56.322 --> 00:26:58.126
Those days are done. I plead the blood over you. Jesus loves you.

00:26:58.127 --> 00:29:01.685
No more torment of PTSD. Anoint your mind with oil too. Jesus knows your heart.

00:29:01.686 --> 00:29:40.514
Surely goodness and mercy will follow you all the days of your life. I call everyone healed, whole, and delivered. Amen.

00:29:40.514 --> 00:29:47.634
If you could, please click the notification bell, like, and subscribe.

00:29:47.635 --> 00:30:09.871
You're helping to get the gospel out and get people saved around the world.

00:30:09.872 --> 00:30:25.159
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you. Bye-bye.

